{"tid":757766,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"溫哥華公共交通工具播放Seth Rogen廣播聲帶","createTime":"2018-07-27T06:13:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-27T06:43:32.000Z","uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f794941d09d997a05e7e8ec506a37f7a37c61cc8","tid":757766,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T06:13:30.000Z","msg":"在溫哥華土生土長的電影演員Seth Rogen，將會為運輸聯線的巴士和架空列車錄製廣播聲帶。<br />\n運輸聯線原本和Visa信用卡合作，安排荷李活影星Morgan Freeman錄製車廂廣播，同時宣傳信用卡直接在入閘機繳付車費的新服務，但是由於Freeman後來面對性不當行為指控，因此計畫被迫取消。<br />\nSeth Rogen後來在Twitter上公開向運輸聯線表示，願意頂替Freeman，錄製聲帶。<br />\n今次Rogen並無收取酬勞，而運輸聯線就負責錄音和製作開支。<br />\n有關廣播將會在下星期推出。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.am1470.com/news_detail.php?i=78533\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am1470.com%2Fnews_detail.php%3Fi%3D78533&d=5SQu4Df4Zm6QU7pBGlGX%2BIM9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=e62f7291\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am1470.com/news_detail.php?i=78533</a>"},{"pid":"f0c3a20cd00cace06132a8d8ea83d749d0ebcd43","tid":757766,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T06:19:03.000Z","msg":"原來香港都有講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5c1b7677c7e06aee92224e6eac7051b86618cd5","tid":757766,"uid":42848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T06:39:02.000Z","msg":"有無加佢啲扯哮笑聲<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=p-9Wcbihsfg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dp-9Wcbihsfg&d=5SQu4Df4Zm6QU7pBGlGX%2BIM9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=d2cc83c3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=p-9Wcbihsfg</a>"},{"pid":"63fc302d1196a29a03f402bcef96597f525579d2","tid":757766,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e5c1b7677c7e06aee92224e6eac7051b86618cd5","tid":757766,"uid":42848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc